fields.name: Venum Contender 5.0 Spats White Camo
fields.description:
The Contender 5.0 Legging can be worn alone or under the Contender 5.0 sports shorts. These compression pants offer many advantages: thin and elastic, they provide an incomparable freedom of movement while protecting from friction thanks to the durability of its fabric. It also facilitates the athletes recovery thanks to the optimal muscular compression.
The second skin effect of leggings or spats makes them extremely comfortable and perfectly suited to many disciplines, from MMA to grappling, wrestling, muay thai or cross-training.

fields.name: Exploration Premium BJJ Shorts
fields.description:
The Exploration Premium BJJ/MMA Shorts feature a striking and vivid image of a ship and sea monster about to engage in an epic battle. These MMA shorts are designed for high intensity training with tear resistant and fast drying fabric. Customize your workout wardrobe with BJJ shorts made to match your body and style.
Mixture of Polyester and Spandex. This makes this highly strong, durable, flexible, stretchable, non-shrinkable and lightweight to give its maximum comfort.

fields.name: Ladies Japan Series Maple Koi GI
fields.description: Following on from the success of the Japan Series Rash Guards, Tatami now introduce to you the same designs in BJJ Gi format. The Maple Koi Gi has the maple koi design printed on the inner jacket. It is manufactured on a black coloured jacket to really make the koi depiction stand out. Also finished off with Japanese embroidered flower emblems, to add a touch off authenticity.

fields.name: Venum Gladiator 3.0 MMA Gloves Matte Black
fields.description:
Venum Gladiator 3.0 MMA Gloves are a perfect combination of quality and style!

They provide maximum protection of the hand, even during your most powerful punches, with a high density foam and specific reinforcements placed on each finger.

The Gladiator 3.0 MMA gloves have a Velcro closure system that provides superior wrist support maximizing the power of strikes and prevention of injuries.

The design of these Venum MMA gloves were created with beautiful graphics inspired by the gladiators.

fields.name: Combat Athletics Essential V2 8oz MMA Sparring Gloves
fields.description: Combat Athletics introduces Version 2 of their Essential range 8oz MMA gloves which are made with synthetic leather DX (Vinyl). Designed using a high compression foam padding and velcro closure; they have been made to ensure a comfortable and safe fitting glove. The MMA gloves also contain an anti bacterial lining, a padded knuckle and thumb and a ventilated palm for cooling comfort.

fields.name: Japanese Torii BJJ Shorts
fields.description:
The Japanese Torii BJJ/MMA Shorts feature the symbol of the land of the rising sun. These MMA shorts are developed to fit a BJJ fighter's intense lifestyle and will withstand any kind of training. Move with a full range of motion in BJJ shorts which don’t restrict or reduce movement. 
Fully sublimated graphics that won't crack, peel, or fade over time and maintain a great look.

fields.name: Hayabusa T3 Kanpeki MMA Gloves 4oz
fields.description:
Perfect Fit and Feel.
The multi-directional Dual-X closure is unmatched when it comes to hand and wrist stabilization for the best protection and injury prevention possible.
Industry-leading Wrist Support.
The best closure system ever created. Hayabusa’s patented wrist support technology helps eliminate hand strain to ensure the best in protection and safety.
Consistent Performance and Durability, Punch after Punch.
Hayabusa gloves are built to last. The attention to detail and craftsmanship guarantees a glove as resilient as the athletes who use it.

fields.name: Scramble Tanren BJJ Belt White

Featuring a few throwbacks in design to the V1 Tanren belt such as some pretty sweet rank bar embroidery and a fancy gold type label (designed to show how fancy and classy your tastes are) this is made to our usual high quality.

fields.name: Red Abyss BJJ Shorts
fields.description:
Perfect your game in the Red Abyss BJJ Shorts. Designed to suit the intense lifestyle of a high performance athlete, these MMA shorts are tear resistant with sublimated graphics that will not fade or peel. Roll and feel your best in BJJ shorts made for comfort and maximum movement.
Optimized for the highest level of athletic performance in BJJ, MMA, catch wrestling, no-gi, and submission grappling.
Multi-panel construction, high-density flat-lock stitching for optimal fit and durability.

fields.name: Ladies Estilo 6.0 Blue & Burgundy
fields.description:
The Estilo is the longest-running and most established BJJ kimono in Tatami Fightwear's fabled gi range. Spanning over 6 years of continuous research, development and improvement - the crown jewel of the model is the Estilo VI, which we are proud to introduce as one of the highest-quality, visually-appealing and well priced BJJ Gi's on the market.
Many of the features of the Estilo 6.0 make it the ultimate kimono for jiujiteros at any experience of ability level. High quality embroideries adorn the shoulders of the gi and the outside leg area of the pants. The classic Estilo logo is subtly placed at the back of the neck and the right shin area of the pants. A small embroidery is placed on the front of the jacket with the "Estilo VI" text. A sublimated neck yoke lining and side bent lining adds high-quality detail to the Estilo - with new unique woven taping to line the inside of the sleeve cuffs, ankle cuffs and the bottom of the jackets.

Designed to fit a fighters intense lifestyle, these MMA shorts are crafted with quality material which lasts no matter how extreme the training. Perfect your game in BJJ shorts that give you full range of motion and movement.
Equipped with an ultra-lightweight and durable perfect stretch fabric.
Inside drawstring & velcro waistband enclosure for a secure fit.
Fully sublimated graphics that will never crack, peel or fade.
Optimized for the highest level of athletic performance in BJJ, MMA, catch wrestling, no-gi, and submission grappling.

fields.name: Valor Victory 2.0 Premium Lightweight BJJ GI White
fields.description:
The Victory 2.0 premium GI is made from a 450gram pearl weave cotton that is lightweight, durable and very comfortable to train in. It is ideal for everyday training and also for competing in. We truly believe that the Victory 2.0 is the best all purpose premium GI.
The GI jacket has a tailored cut so it fits closer to the body giving it a better fit than most standard GIs. It features contrast stitching, stylish Valor embroideries, branded woven tape inside the sleeve and trouser cuffs and a sublimated neck yoke.

fields.name: Tatami Fightwear Essential 3.0 Long Sleeve Rash Guard Black Grey
fields.description:
This is the latest in a line of Tatami No Gi apparel that is astutely designed for style, comfort and above all else – functional performance. With fresh looks, we aim to get you looking the part as well as giving you the tools to get the best out of your game.
As one of our most popular collections, the latest Essentials range has been redesigned with a contemporary design. A sliced rectangle Tatami logo covers the middle of the chest with a bold stripe adorning the outside of the sleeve of each arm.
The rash guard is made with the usual high quality of Tatami training gear. With a polyester-spandex fabric blend, the rash guard is designed to hold up against the rigours of everyday training, in particular against tough pulling. The artwork is fully sublimated to ensure the durability and look of the design.

fields.description:
Bring intensity to the mat with the War BJJ Shorts. Reach your true potential with style and comfort in a pair of MMA shorts designed for maximum movement. These BJJ shorts are created to withstand intense training, letting you focus on your roll without fear of tearing. 
Optimized for the highest level of athletic performance in BJJ, MMA, catch wrestling, no-gi, and submission grappling.

fields.name: Yokkao Vintage Carbon Shorts Red Gold
fields.description:
The YOKKAO Vintage Carbon Shorts Red Gold are the perfect pair of shorts for anyone training in Muay Thai and Kickboxing.

The shorts feature the YOKKAO logo across the front along with bright stars on the side.

They are specifically cut with wide leg room to aid in mobility and comfort specifically for training Muay Thai.

fields.name: Venum Skull Short Sleeve Rash Guard
fields.description:
Perfect for MMA, grappling or wrestling, the Skull Rash guard sports a magnificent skull. This compression shirt optimizes recovery. It also provides a protective role by limiting friction to the skin, something that often goes hand in hand with combat sports.
The silicone band located at the waist prevents the Rash guard from rising throughout training.
Specifically adapted to the constraints of combat sports, rash guards remain multidisciplinary training outfits that will delight any athlete looking for performance!

fields.name: Model X Jiu Jitsu Gi - Blue
fields.description:
The technical make-up of the X makes it ideal for training and competition. With a 250GSM jacket and 7oz ripstop pants, the lightweight nature of the gi supports your movement and doesn’t feel like it’s weighing you down in the heat of the roll. This, along with curved vents and a competition cut, means the X is geared towards giving you the most comfortable and efficient fit without sacrificing any strength or durability.

With the core colours of white, blue and black, each version of the X uses red stitching to create a sharp and modernistic colour contrast. An exclusive X logo is proudly presented on the shoulders, lapel, neck and leg along with the classic Tatami logo to create a versatile look.

fields.name: Tatami Fightwear Essential Mens BJJ Gi Blue
fields.description: The Essential Gi range is the latest in high-quality, performance driven BJJ kimonos from Tatami Fightwear. Designed for optimum comfort and manoeuvrability, the Essential Gi is lightweight with 250GSM Pearl Weave Jacket and 7oz ripstop pants to ensure no extra heavy baggage as you train and compete. The light nature of the gi does not come at the cost of any strength or resistance. There are 4 rows of reinforcement areas that stand up to rigorous rolling.

fields.name: Nova Absolute Black Gi
fields.description:
Tatami Fightwear are proud to introduce the Nova Absolute, a culmination of years of hard work and development to create one of our most iconic Gi’s. The Nova Gi is a staple of the Tatami Fightwear range and comes with a strong tradition of offering style and comfort for training and competing at exceptional value.
In order to make the Nova Absolute one of the most diverse and complete Gi’s on the market, we engaged in extensive research amongst not only casual practitioners but all the way up to world class competitors to find out what people look for as they search fpr the perfect Gi for themselves.

fields.name: Scramble Verano Sports Leggings Green
fields.description: The blue, white and red set coordinates perfectly and is expertly colourmatched and designed so as not to be too overwhelming when worn as part of a set. These premium spats will outlast any grappling session.

fields.name: Venum Womens One FC Impact Short Sleeve Rash Guard Grey Yellow
fields.description:
The ONE FC Impact rashguard for women is ideal for practicing combat sports but also for fitness.
This “second skin” effect t-shirt contributes to active muscle recovery thanks to its pressure zones in the muscles of the bust and arms.
Tightly fitting, this compression shirt limits friction and protects your skin during training.
Very stretchy and very soft, this extremely fitted t-shirt is also equipped with large mesh panels which facilitate the wicking of perspiration.
ONE FC is one of the world's largest combat sports organizations. Broadcast in over 128 countries, this promotion organizes MMA, Muay Thai and kickboxing bouts. ONE FC brings together the greatest specialists across these disciplines, including Angela Lee, Giorgio Petrosyan, Samy Sana, Élias Mamhoudi, Sitthichai and Bobo Sacko.
This model measures 169 cm, weighs 62 kg and wears a size S product. Her chest measurement is 96 cm and her waist measurement is 74 cm.

fields.name: Ladies Black Zero G V4 Advanced Lightweight Gi
fields.description:
Tatami Fightwear introduces the Womens Zero G V4 BJJ GI. After months of design and testing Tatami Fightwear are proud to introduce their Zero G V4. If you have liked the previous incarnations of the Zero G you'll love the Zero G V4.
Tatami Fightwear's Zero G V4 BJJ GI has been designed in conjunction with some of the worlds best BJJ athletes such as 2017 ADCC Champion JT Torres, Vitor 'Shaolin' Ribeiro, Robson Moura and Michelle Nicolini.
The Zero G V4 is constructed so that the design, durability, and fit across all sizes is the best it can be. The Zero G V4 with jacket and pants weighs just 1.5kilo making it one a fantastic competition and daily Jiu Jitsu Gi.

fields.name: Fumentsu Ghost MMA Sparring Glove
fields.description: Fumetsu Ghost MMA Sparring Gloves provide maximum protection, safety and comfort during your MMA training. The padded knuckle area is similar to that of a boxing glove ensuring protection for both you and your training partner. The open palm ensures full range of movement when grappling, extra padding on the thumb adds to the overall protection of the glove, making this the whole package.

fields.name: Tatami Ladies Classic Gi - White
fields.description:
Constantly striving to break boundaries on BJJ apparel - we introduce to you the Tatami Fightwear Classic Ladies Gi. A minimalist gi packed with clever technical details to keep you looking fresh and give you the extra edge as you take to the mat.

We’ve worked tirelessly researching and developing to make the Classic gi the ultimate competition gi.

The jacket contains a dual weave construction. A middle seam covered with interior canvas taping separates the top and bottom half. The top half has a tough and heavier 550GSM pearl weave fabric with the bottom a 350GSM that means the jacket sits lighter on your body and ensures a more comfortable fit.

fields.name: Juzo Flex Genu XTRA Knee Support
fields.description: The JuzoFlex Genu Xtra knee support adapts to every movement without losing it's shape, so it can provide effective support and relief to the knee joint. The Xtra Fabric from Juzo is made using their unique 3D knitting technology. This special technology ensures optimal moisture regulation and breathability, combined with maximised freedom of movement and support for joints and muscles. The all-rounder for everyday life, work and sport!

fields.name: Tatami Fightwear Ladies Tropic Long Sleeve Rash Guard Black
fields.description:
Tatami Fightwear introduces the SS20 no gi range which continues to innovate on-the-mat aesthetics and functionality.

Our new styles of rash guards, shorts and spats take centre stage in defining your training or competition gear, while being designed and manufactured with the purpose of optimising your performance.

Part of the Tropic collection, the Ladies Tropic rash guard comes in black with grey print
colour scheme. The Tropic design features a core front side with a kanji print alongside and a tropical themed back bar that is also represented on the sleeves.

The rash guards are made from a polyester-spandex fabric blend that holds strong even
under the pressures of pulling and stretching with fully sublimated printing that protects the look.

fields.description: The blue, white and red set coordinates perfectly and is expertly colourmatched and designed so as not to be too overwhelming when worn as part of a set. These premium spats will outlast every intense grappling session.
